LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:ActionBar"

\end_inset

, which can perform actions to the application.
 It has been around for a long time and is one of the most recognizable
 patterns
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Lehtimaeki2013"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

